Reclusa::

She let her head lower. SHe took a deep breath. "Perhaps it is just
not my place, my lord. But I am troubled to see you so up set. Well,
really ticked off would be a better term for it."  She let her regal
stance soften a bit. Beyond her understanding, it did bother her that
her leader, one that projected such strength and wisdom would be so
angry at things. For some dumb reason, it really did bother her. She
made to mental note to have her circuits and programs checked later.
She raised her head and regained her regal composure. "I just wish
there was something I could do." she said in a soft tone. One could
almost hear the caring if one listened closely enough.  

Per her programs, bots, all bots, were expendable, save herself of
course. Even leaders could come and go as fate desided. It never
bothered her before, why should he matter, but for reasons beyond her
understanding, it did.
